{"id":"api/platform-server","title":"@angular/platform-server","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/platform-server\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-server\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-server/PACKAGE.md\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n<header class=\"api-header\">\n  <h1 id=\"angularplatform-server\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2hyttbmyr2op7zb3isl7qcjo\">@angular/platform-server<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#angularplatform-server\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n  <label class=\"api-type-label package\">package</label>\n  \n  \n  \n</header>\n\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\"><p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"70wgt22w1b4kj92srhqygcbbn\">支援在服務器上交付 Angular 應用程式，用於\n<a href=\"guide/glossary#server-side-rendering\">伺服器端渲染</a>（SSR）。</p>\n\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"31cpsqwhhum3hnm7diiy6agai\">有關更多訊息，請參見\n<a href=\"guide/ssr\">伺服器端渲染：Angular SSR 簡介</a>。</p>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n<h2 id=\"entry-points\">入口點<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#entry-points\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"主要\">主要<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#主要\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"primary\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"fkfm2umomg24u7zlbw0i7dqq\">主要<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#primary\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server#primary-entry-point-exports\">@angular/platform-server</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"70wgt22w1b4kj92srhqygcbbn\">支援在服務器上交付 Angular 應用程式，用於\n<a href=\"guide/glossary#server-side-rendering\">伺服器端渲染</a>（SSR）。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"次要\">次要<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#次要\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"secondary\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"qmb2o62wilek3owziq44q5ie\">次要<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#secondary\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/init\">@angular/platform-server/init</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4p2wvdge9kdgczpnpar4a9b8g\">初始化用於呈現 Angular 應用程式的伺服器環境。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/testing\">@angular/platform-server/testing</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3l14h8q375vovaeagqvfvo6sx\">為 Angular 平台伺服器子系統提供測試模組。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<h2 id=\"primary-entry-point-exports\">主要入口點的匯出<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#primary-entry-point-exports\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"ngmodules\">NgModules<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#ngmodules\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/ServerModule\">ServerModule</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c8ki9jj9o22gaobmpej23tlk2\">伺服器的 ng 模組。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor deprecated-api-item\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule\" class=\"deprecated-api-item\">ServerTransferStateModule</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          <p><strong>已棄用:</strong> no longer needed, you can inject the <code><a href=\"api/core/TransferState\" class=\"code-anchor\">TransferState</a></code> in an app without providing\nthis module.</p>\n\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1n76uiug7l75y4u4u7bog3ef9\">要安裝在服務端的 NgModule，它同時會使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/TransferState\" class=\"code-anchor\">TransferState</a></code> 將狀態從伺服器傳輸到用戶端。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"類\">類<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#類\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"classes\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dtpuzegyjmcbul5yz5jn1ham3\">類<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#classes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformState\">PlatformState</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6mqxkbghsjvu2wvhboi1mlqd\">當前平台狀態的表示形式。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"函式\">函式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#函式\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"functions\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dt2uvbdl3r7k4tmkiulzt8lb8\">函式<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#functions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/provideServerRendering\">provideServerRendering</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3s19s0wyq4vrlnifj4zg847fn\">設定為應用程式啟用伺服器端渲染功能所需的提供程式。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication\">renderApplication</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6lc06kjeucaqddclcb0s5m2gu\">引導 Angular 應用程式的實例並將其渲染為字串。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderModule\">renderModule</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9fxmc7lk2wfdckj5ftratt5nb\">使用提供的 NgModule 引導應用程式，並將頁面內容序列化為字串。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"結構\">結構<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#結構\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"structures\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2pvj0r4hennzfp5hvt5swfw10\">結構<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#structures\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/PlatformConfig\">PlatformConfig</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"2np7asw1tmhtmpqbomuwq9b4z\">傳遞設定物件以初始化平台。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"export-list\">\n    <h3 translation-result=\"on\" id=\"型別\">型別<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#型別\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"types\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"edj3fs52fiqyg9u6mdyxchcwv\">型別<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server#types\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n    <table class=\"is-full-width list-table\">\n      \n      <tbody><tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/BEFORE_APP_SERIALIZED\">BEFORE_APP_SERIALIZED</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5q6jg3rlelgcvmz3axu4e4lex\">在當前平台狀態渲染為字串之前呼叫 <code><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">renderApplication</a></code> 或 <code><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">renderModule</a></code> 時將執行的函式。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/INITIAL_CONFIG\">INITIAL_CONFIG</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1vuc2our5vf7qf7pp2gw98rfn\">DI 令牌，用於設定平台的初始設定。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor deprecated-api-item\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/platformDynamicServer\" class=\"deprecated-api-item\">platformDynamicServer</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          <p><strong>已棄用:</strong> add an <code>import @angular/compiler</code> and replace the usage with <code><a href=\"api/platform-server/platformServer\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformServer</a></code>\ninstead.</p>\n\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cshjnj444pm2egir1fqoz754a\">支援執行時編譯器的伺服器平台。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr>\n        <td><code class=\"code-anchor\"><a href=\"api/platform-server/platformServer\">platformServer</a></code></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      \n    </tbody></table>\n  </section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-server/BEFORE_APP_SERIALIZED\n - api/platform-server/INITIAL_CONFIG\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig\n - api/platform-server/PlatformState\n - api/platform-server/ServerModule\n - api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule\n - api/platform-server/init\n - api/platform-server/platformDynamicServer\n - api/platform-server/platformServer\n - api/platform-server/provideServerRendering\n - api/platform-server/renderApplication\n - api/platform-server/renderModule\n - api/platform-server/testing\n - api/platform-server/testing/ServerTestingModule\n - api/platform-server/testing/platformServerTesting\n - guide/glossary\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/TransferState\n - api/platform-server#\n - api/platform-server#angularplatform-server\n - api/platform-server#classes\n - api/platform-server#entry-points\n - api/platform-server#functions\n - api/platform-server#ngmodules\n - api/platform-server#primary\n - api/platform-server#primary-entry-point-exports\n - api/platform-server#secondary\n - api/platform-server#structures\n - api/platform-server#types\n - api/platform-server#主要\n - api/platform-server#函式\n - api/platform-server#次要\n - api/platform-server#類\n - api/platform-server#型別\n - api/platform-server#結構\n - api/platform-server/BEFORE_APP_SERIALIZED\n - api/platform-server/INITIAL_CONFIG\n - api/platform-server/PlatformConfig\n - api/platform-server/PlatformState\n - api/platform-server/ServerModule\n - api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule\n - api/platform-server/init\n - api/platform-server/platformDynamicServer\n - api/platform-server/platformServer\n - api/platform-server/provideServerRendering\n - api/